OL,3,CShropshire fire crews respond to four
OL,4,Csuspected arsons in one hour
OL,6,FFire crews in Shropshire say they
OL,7,Fbelieve four fires within a mile of
OL,8,Feach other in the early hours of
OL,9,FSaturday morning were all linked.
OL,11,FFirefighters in Market Drayton were
OL,12,Fcalled to Longslow Road just after
OL,13,Fmidnight, where they extinguished a
OL,14,Ffire in a commercial wheelie bin.
OL,16,FShortly after they were alerted to a
OL,17,Fsecond fire at an address on Longslow
OL,18,FRoad, which involved two wheelie bins
OL,19,Fand a wooden garden shed.
