OL,3,CShropshire fire crews respond to four
OL,4,Csuspected arsons in one hour
OL,6,FAs crews were damping down they were
OL,7,Fthen called to another incident on
OL,8,FPortland Drive. Officers say two
OL,9,Fwheelie bins were destroyed by the
OL,10,Fblaze and damage was also caused to
OL,11,Ftwo garages and two vehicles.
OL,13,FWhilst the Market Drayton crew was
OL,14,Fdealing with the fire on Portland
OL,15,FDrive, the service was made aware of
OL,16,Fanother fire on Elm Drive, involving
OL,17,Fwheelie bins and a vehicle. This
OL,18,Fincident was dealt with by crews from
OL,19,FHodnet.
