OL,3,CShropshire fire crews respond to four
OL,4,Csuspected arsons in one hour
OL,6,FMarket Drayton Fire Service said in a
OL,7,Fpost on social media that it believes
OL,8,Fall of the incidents are linked and it
OL,9,Fis appealing for information and
OL,10,Fdoorbell or CCTV footage.
OL,12,F"All of these fires are believed to be
OL,13,Flinked and started deliberately," the
OL,14,Fservice said.
OL,16,F"If you have any information, doorbell
OL,17,For security camera footage that may
OL,18,Fhelp with investigations please call
OL,19,F101 to report it."
